title: Wide receiver Dez Bryant is doubtful | Dallas Cowboys vs. Giants injury report
text:
Comments 
EAST RUTHERFORD â€” It does not look like Dallas Cowboys wide receiver Dez Bryant will be back on the field this Sunday against the Giants . 
Bryant did not practice again on Wednesday, and the Cowboys listed him as doubtful for this weekend's game at MetLife Stadium as he works his way back from a broken foot suffered against the Giants in Week 1 . 
Cowboys coach Jason Garrett has said Bryant will have to practice before he plays in a game. The Cowboys still have a Saturday walkthrough though, and all indications are Bryant will make the trip to New Jersey. So, things can always change . But for now, it looks like Bryant will be out.
